<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="brand-mark">焕</view>
    <view class="title">焕发</view>
    <view class="subtitle">同一个小程序，顾客试发和商家经营分开使用</view>
  </view>

  <view class="mode-list">
    <view class="mode-card" bindtap="enterCustomer">
      <view>
        <view class="mode-title">顾客体验</view>
        <view class="mode-desc">上传自拍、选择发型发色、生成试发方案并预约到店</view>
      </view>
      <view class="mode-action">进入</view>
    </view>

    <view class="mode-card merchant" bindtap="enterMerchant">
      <view>
        <view class="mode-title">商家工作台</view>
        <view class="mode-desc">查看预约订单、顾客、素材、团队和门店数据</view>
      </view>
      <view class="mode-action">进入</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="tip">
    当前为合并版测试入口。正式上线后会根据微信身份自动进入对应模式。
  </view>
</view>
